attributes.Long form description: The student assembles the utility cart. First assembles the base frame. Then inserts the bottom legs and screws them. Next, he assembles the top legs. Then places the bottom grid tray, assembles in place the middle grid tray and assembles the top grid tray. After that screws the middle grid tray. At last, he assembles the four wheels.
